      </p>
      <p> 
        Otherwise, these are the specific roles we need help with on Friday 7th July 2023.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label accent-border">
      <h3 class="section-title">Registration &amp; information</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="card accent-border">
      <p>Recruiting 2 more volunteers.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Manage the registration desk activities such has handing out lanyards to registered attendees</li>
        <li>Respond to general enquiries</li>
        <li>Manage main entrance to conference room. Ensure that no one can enter in the middle of a talk and disrupt stage activities.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label accent-border">
      <h3 class="section-title">Catering</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="card accent-border">
      <p>Recruiting 3 more volunteers.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Arrange catering layout and food labelling on the day of the event</li>
        <li>Manage the coffee station</li>
        <li>Ensure that dietary requirements are met</li>
        <li>Manage the crowd by responding to food-related queries during morning tea, afternoon tea and lunch</li>
        <li>Pack up catering</li>
        <li>Facilitate after socials venue</li>
        <li>Submit catering-related expenses</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfIEBKP2Oozb5XVyIJD_VQCB1Iw37P5GX-QnBnniZZ6S7FNXA/viewform?usp=sf_link" rel="external" class="button">Volunteer at NZ Tech Rally 2023 for one day</a>
